Biography

Coach Barboto on Martinez Cubel: "A very special 1v1 player in the run of play. He is elusive on the dribble and has the courage in and around the goal to shoot and score."

2023: Saw action in 14 matches, including nine starts. ... recorded two goals, one assist for five points.

2022: Appeared in 15 matches, including eight starts. ... combined for a pair of assists in his first season at NJIT. ... first collegiate assist vs. Sacred Heart (9.20.22).

Prior to NJIT: Martinez Cubel joins the Highlanders from Spain where he played for Valencia CF Academy. He served as a team captain of the u19 team in Spain in addition to being named as an Elite Athlete.

Personal: Sergio Martinez Cubel. ... son of Vincente Martinez Zaballos and Concepcion Cubel Villanueva. ... graduated with honors from Colegio Nuestra Senora del Socorro high school ... industrial engineering major.
